name: All Twice SD 1,5
description:
Hi, This is my Attempt at making an CKPT for a kpop Girl Group T*ice, IYKYK.

Training Data :

  • Trained using HQ picture from Twitter Fanbase

  • Cropped to 512x512 image

  • Handpicked image at my liking (trying to cover all possible angle and expression)

  • Each Person has 45 Image equal, so thats 9*45 Images

  • Trained on dreambooth local without EMA using nonpruned 1,5 SD base model, fp16, Xformers

  • using 100 Epoch

  • Uploaded the best CKPT IMO at 88210 Steps. i'll try to upload a lower steps CKPT or higher.

This model Seems to generate subpar image of J*ong, D*hyun and J*hyo, but it produce great result for the other members. ( for j*hyo i find using the restore face really fix her eye bag by alot)

This model is bad to be used As is, but will produce great result if you merge it with your own model (i suspect because my training data have limited full body image) ill upload an merger and unmerged example

Sample #1 is X/Y Plot using the base CKPT without Merge

Sample #2 is X/Y Plot using the base CKPT Merged with Analogdiffusion

Sample #3 is X/Y Plot using the base CKPT Merged with Anything 3.0

Sample #4 is X/Y Plot using the base CKPT Merged with URPM
